queue
Interface Queue<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the element type.
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayQueue, NodeQueue
public interface Queue<E>

The Queue class represents a FIFO (first-in-first-out) set of objects. The usual enqueue and dequeue operations are provided, as well as a method to peek at the front item on the queue, a method to test for whether the queue is empty and a method that returns the queue's size.
